                      "ep_id": 11,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Beidou_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "北斗",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器白值很低，因此會比較依賴於武器的副詞條。攜帶該武器的北斗能提高",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，且武器技能可以為全隊角色充能，也是副C北斗的一種選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 40,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Noelle_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "諾艾爾",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器能在很大程度上提高諾艾爾的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，但相比於其他四星武器（例如白影劍等），它缺乏數值提升和傷害增加，因此諾艾爾的傷害會大幅降低。要仔細斟酌後再決定是否給諾艾爾使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 21,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Sayu_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "早柚",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器提供了較高的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "和大量元素微粒，雖然沒有直接提供攻擊力或者元素精通來為早柚提高治療量，但也提高了早柚釋放元素爆發的頻率，在無其他選擇時可以讓早柚佩戴。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
